Params: {1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory79.jpg'}
{2: 'System', 3: '"This way to the palace."'}
{3: 'There was a wooden sign on the side of the road. The direction on the sign pointed to a castle-like building.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Vera', 3: 'So are we going there to find the King and pick up quests from him?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Camu', 3: "So much hassle. Why don't they just tell me who to kill.", 4: '2'}
{2: "Perhaps we don't have to kill anyone.", 3: '9', 4: "Perhaps there will be some enemy we can't beat.", 5: '10'}
{2: 'Camu', 3: "I'm going to kill the King if he gives us those weird errands quests.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Vera', 3: "Oh really? I'm keen to meet that enemy.", 4: '1'}
{3: 'No matter what, all three of them seemed to be the "bold" type.'}
{2: 'Vera', 3: 'Why are you sighing? Are you tired, 【kuroname】?', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Vera turned to me, pretending to be caring. But I still saw that same mocking smile on her face.'}
{2: 'Vera', 3: '"If 【kuroname】 is tired, we\'ll just leave you. The system never forced us to move together."', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: 'Oh, right. I went quite far away when I was scouting on my own.', 4: '3'}
{3: "I hadn't said anything, but they were already thinking of abandoning their teammates."}
{2: 'Wait, I can walk!', 3: '17', 4: "Don't you know teammates are extremely important in role-playing games?", 5: '19'}
{2: 'Vera', 3: "Good. I don't want to lose such a good shield yet.", 4: '1'}
{3: 'She said shield, but I decided to just pretend as if I heard nothing.'}
{2: 'Camu', 3: 'Teammates? Do you mean yourself, or the other two useless Constructs?', 4: '2'}
{3: 'I wanted to argue back, but Camu was right. This team was just too imbalanced.'}
{2: 'Vera', 3: "Anyway, 【kuroname】 seems to be in good spirits. Let's get to the palace before night comes.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Camu', 3: "I agree. Let's go, hmph.", 4: '2'}
